ttps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/telltale-games-laid-off-most-of-its-employees-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/telltale-games-laid-off-most-of-its-employees-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/telltale-games-laid-off-most-of-its-employees-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/telltale-games-laid-off-most-of-its-employees-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/telltale-games">Telltale Games</a>正在开发即将推出的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-wolf-among-us-2">《我们身边的狼 2》</a> ，</em>据称该公司在 9 月份解雇了“大部分”员工。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/slamdunk-festival-2023-video-games-bowling-for-soup-underoath-heriot-we-came-as-romans-3442102">电子游戏如何让你最喜欢的乐队在旅途中保持理智</a></strong></li></ul><p>这一说法来自该工作室的前电影艺术家乔纳·黄 (Jonah Huang)，他在<a href="https://x.com/jjonahjonahson/status/1709979363608039784?s=20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X（fka Twitter）的帖子</a>中发布了这一消息。</p><p> “这是一个令人痛心的话题，但我觉得有必要补充一下游戏业裁员的消息：Telltale 在 9 月初解雇了我们大多数人，”他声称。 “ <em>TWAU2</em>的状态，我不能透露（保密协议）。” </p><figure id="attachment_3510699" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3510699" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3510699" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/telltale-games-laid-off-most-of-its-employees-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/telltale-games-laid-off-most-of-its-employees-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/telltale-games-laid-off-most-of-its-employees-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/telltale-games-laid-off-most-of-its-employees-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/telltale-games-laid-off-most-of-its-employees-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp